Class DefaultJaxbConverterRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.spi.jaxb.transport.DefaultJaxbConverterRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JaxbConverterRegistry

    public class DefaultJaxbConverterRegistry
extends Object
implements JaxbConverterRegistry
    Default JaxbConverterRegistry implementation, using reflection Converter instances to convert back and forth between JAXB-annotated transport types.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
